# Dev server (`npm run dev`) talks to the LIVE MI Agent API via the Vite proxy
# (see vite.config.ts: /mi + /health -> http://localhost:8000). Same-origin, so
# no CORS — works in Codespaces. This makes `npm run dev` use real data by default.
#
# Want the offline demo instead? Create .env.development.local (git-ignored) with:
#   VITE_AGENT_MODE=mock
VITE_AGENT_API_URL=/
